fullplot: A hot shot Washington DC lobbyist and his protègè go down hard as their schemes to peddle influence lead to corruption and murder.
plot: A hot shot Washington DC lobbyist and his protègè go down hard as their schemes to peddle influence lead to corruption and murder.
title: Casino Jack

tomatoes.consensus: Kevin Spacey turns in one of his stronger performances, but Casino Jack is a disappointingly uneven fictionalized account of a fascinating true story.
